  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The hit kite fighting game is now available on PC!</strong><br>This game is <strong>cross-platform</strong>, so you can play with your friends on mobile.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Raise your kite and challenge the best in the skies!</strong><br>Engage in epic aerial battles by controlling a <strong>kite</strong> and challenging players from around the world. Show off your skills by cutting enemy lines and claiming your spot at the top. Victory depends on your <strong>angle</strong>, your <strong>line</strong>, and your <strong>technique</strong>. Do you have what it takes to conquer the skies?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851200/extras/2bb49c14986061625295b318385cd6b4.poster.avif?t=1768923900\" width=800 height=454 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851200/extras/2bb49c14986061625295b318385cd6b4.webm?t=1768923900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851200/extras/2bb49c14986061625295b318385cd6b4.mp4?t=1768923900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 <strong>Strategy and Aerial Combat</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cut enemy lines:</strong> Outsmart your opponents with precise maneuvers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect fallen kites:</strong> Claim the trophies of your victories for rewards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cut tails:</strong> A special technique for expert players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inspired Mode:</strong> Cut through a storm of enemy kites and activate powerful bonuses!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dominate the rankings:</strong> Reach the Top 3 in maps, lines, and rooms.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achieve the impossible:</strong> Cut strong lines with a weaker line to gain advantages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Break enemy kites:</strong> Unlock exclusive bonuses.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Intuitive and Dynamic Controls</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Release:</strong> Loosen the line to make the kite turn gently.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quick release:</strong> Quickly loosen the line to send the kite away fast.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pull the line:</strong> Advance and control the direction with precision.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Disbique:</strong> Perform sharp and dominant moves to gain an edge in battle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>Progression and Rewards</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn <strong>gold</strong> and <strong>experience</strong> to improve your skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock epic combos like <strong>double</strong>, <strong>triple</strong>, <strong>quadra</strong>, <strong>penta</strong>, and <strong>hexa</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The road to greatness won’t be easy. Find the perfect combination of <strong>kite</strong> and <strong>line</strong> to become a true master of kite combat. Download now and show who rules the skies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851200/extras/661fbe4e0b1c426cc3ff93eeacf815b7.poster.avif?t=1768923900\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851200/extras/661fbe4e0b1c426cc3ff93eeacf815b7.webm?t=1768923900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851200/extras/661fbe4e0b1c426cc3ff93eeacf815b7.mp4?t=1768923900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💡 <strong>Important:</strong><br>The game uses your <strong>SteamID</strong> for data registration, which means it is <strong>not connected to the account server of the mobile version</strong>.</p>",
